{"consensus_set_id":"55810","translation_language":"fa","translation_source":{"hid":"408128"},"segments":[{"source_hadith_segment":"فِي قَوْلِهِ :   <quranic_text> « وَ اِذْ قٰالَ مُوسيٰ لِفَتٰاهُ » </quranic_text>   <footnote> [ الكهف ۶۰ ] </footnote>  قَالَ :  « هُوَ يُوشَعُ بْنُ نُونٍ وَ قَوْلُهُ :   <quranic_text> « لاٰ اَبْرَحُ » </quranic_text>   <footnote> [ الكهف ۶۰ ] </footnote>  يَقُولُ :  لاَ اَزَالُ  <quranic_text> « حَتّٰي اَبْلُغَ مَجْمَعَ الْبَحْرَيْنِ اَوْ اَمْضِيَ حُقُباً » </quranic_text>   <footnote> [ الكهف ۶۰ ] </footnote> - قَالَ - الْحُقُبُ ثَمَانُونَ سَنَةً وَ قَوْلُهُ :   <quranic_text> « لَقَدْ جِئْتَ شَيْئاً اِمْراً » </quranic_text>   <footnote> [ الكهف ۷۱ ] </footnote>  هُوَ الْمُنْكَرُ ،  وَ كَانَ مُوسَي ( عَلَيْهِ السَّلاَمُ ) يُنْكِرُ الظُّلْمَ ،  فَاَعْظَمَ مَا رَاَي »","translation_segment":"","segment_columns":[{"kind":"word","token":"في","display":"فِي"},{"kind":"word","token":"قوله","display":"قَوْلِهِ"},{"kind":"tag_open","tag_name":"quranic_text"},{"kind":"word","token":"و","display":"وَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"اذ","display":"اِذْ"},{"kind":"word","token":"قال","display":"قٰالَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"موسي","display":"مُوسيٰ"},{"kind":"word","token":"لفتاه","display":"لِفَتٰاهُ"},{"kind":"tag_close","tag_name":"quranic_text"},{"kind":"tag_open","tag_name":"footnote"},{"kind":"word","token":"الكهف","display":"الكهف"},{"kind":"word","token":"۶۰","display":"۶۰"},{"kind":"tag_close","tag_name":"footnote"},{"kind":"word","token":"قال","display":"قَالَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"هو","display":"هُوَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"يوشع","display":"يُوشَعُ"},{"kind":"word","token":"بن","display":"بْنُ"},{"kind":"word","token":"نون","display":"نُونٍ"},{"kind":"word","token":"و","display":"وَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"قوله","display":"قَوْلُهُ"},{"kind":"tag_open","tag_name":"quranic_text"},{"kind":"word","token":"لا","display":"لاٰ"},{"kind":"word","token":"ابرح","display":"اَبْرَحُ"},{"kind":"tag_close","tag_name":"quranic_text"},{"kind":